### PROTECTED ROUTES (Authentication Required - Organizer/Admin)
### ============================================================

### Create New Nominee
# The nominee_code is auto-generated (4-character alphanumeric code)
POST {{baseUrl}}/nominees/award-categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
    "name": "New Nominee Name",
    "description": "Description of the nominee and their achievements",
    "display_order": 5
}

